casebody.data:
Joseph WHITE, et ux., petitioners,
v.
ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MICHIGAN. No. 16-7592. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 27, 2017.

Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioners allowed until March 20, 2017, within *1220which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
